w.nme.com/news/music/watch-bts-jungkook-and-latto-perform-seven-at-global-citizen-2023-3503319">《Seven》</a> ，其中有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/latto">Latto</a>的身影，以及上个月由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jungkook-jack-harlow-single-3d-3503479">Jack Harlow 演唱的《3D》</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-kid-laroi-too-much-bts-jungkook-central-cee-3511644">The Kid Laroi 与 BTS 的 Jungkook 和 Central Cee 合作推出新单曲《Too Much》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
